# Copy to `.env` (gitignored) if you need to override defaults locally.
# The mobile app does not read process.env at runtime — Plane credentials are
# entered on the in-app setup screen and stored via expo-secure-store.
#
# EAS Build DOES NOT upload .env to the build server (it's excluded by design),
# so this file is really only useful for local overrides via app.config.js.

# Optional: path to Firebase google-services.json for Android FCM push.
# Defaults to ./google-services.json when omitted (see ./credentials/README.md).
# GOOGLE_SERVICES_JSON=./google-services.json
